NAME
    select - query records with field selection

SYNOPSIS
    select <fields> [from <path>]

DESCRIPTION
    Queries records and displays selected fields in table format.
    Fields are comma-separated. Path defaults to current directory.

EXAMPLES
    select id, name
        Select from current directory

    select id, name from users
        Select from relative path

    select id, email from /api/data/users
        Select from absolute path

    select *
        Select all fields (not yet supported)

OUTPUT
    Results displayed in formatted table with headers.

SEE ALSO
    describe, cat, ls
